{"tid":518343,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"通了！北韓主動撥電話聯繫南韓 時隔近2年首破冰","createTime":"2018-01-03T08:31:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-03T15:50:08.000Z","uid":39464,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"593869d7cacb859fbb87e0be088526e3541a51a1","tid":518343,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T08:31:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpmtOIBm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpmtOIBm.jpg&h=4d12d54e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n北韓在台灣時間下午2點30分撥打電話給南韓，確認電話和傳真機是否正常。（美聯社）<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕北韓領導人金正恩在新年致詞時向南韓釋出善意，並表態願派出代表團參加平昌冬奧，雙方更在今日下午重啟熱線，這也是自2016年2月雙邊斷線後首次通話。<br />\n<br />\n根據《韓聯社》報導，北韓在今日宣布，下午將重啟兩韓熱線。南韓統一部指出，台灣時間下午2點30分，雙方透過板門店聯絡官通話，電話由北韓撥打，主要是確認電話和傳真是否能正常運作。<br />\n<br />\n報導中提到，這是雙方自2016年2月開城工業區停運後，時隔1年11個月的首次通話。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2301395\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2301395&d=tPtgdxispHM4pG8INjHj0ZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=a98baa66\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2301395&h=a92ee5fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2301395</a>"},{"pid":"419cdedfcce14c50cc90fe7224bb4e1b916de3dd","tid":518343,"uid":63,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T08:39:28.000Z","msg":"又r 綜援<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n南泡個垃圾總統肯定奶晒金仔袋底<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6db9816e3eeae1923099754e533b38e2e8c5a957","tid":518343,"uid":85461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T08:39:52.000Z","msg":"唔係話射核彈咩"},{"pid":"3519b6f10fc3002ea85207b114b96cb729f9757b","tid":518343,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyT